@startuml
title Boltzmann (Softmax) Exploration Strategy

class BoltzmannAgent {
  +temperature: float
  +selectAction(actions: List<Action>): Action
}

class Action {
  <<data>>
  +actionType: String
  +estimatedValue: float
}

class SoftmaxSelector {
  +computeProbabilities(actions: List<Action>, temperature: float): List<float>
  +selectBasedOnProbability(actions: List<Action>, probabilities: List<float>): Action
}

' Relationships
BoltzmannAgent --> SoftmaxSelector : uses (Softmax Computation)

note right of BoltzmannAgent
  1. Compute softmax probabilities
  2. Select action probabilistically
end note

@enduml
